{"tid":603232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞幫「妖域」 圍毆3德遊客","createTime":"2018-03-23T14:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T14:38:15.000Z","uid":93839,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d355b710539d2ad38f6dbd996dfdd472a3c453","tid":603232,"uid":93839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:31:43.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】南亞幫暴打遊客損港聲譽！被稱為「人間妖域」的中環蘭桂坊，昨凌晨有一批南亞漢在酒吧內，借意向三名德國籍遊客挑釁後，乘三名遊客離開時，隨即在街頭撲出圍攻。三名遊客被打致頭破血流受傷，兇徒逞兇後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n酒吧職員見狀報警，大批警員接報到場，先行安排三名傷者由救護員送院，並在現場兜截兇徒，但毫無發現。其後，翻查現場附近「天眼」，掌握線索追兇，七名兇徒年約廿五至卅五歲；案列襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，由中區警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>女子秀茂坪遇南亞淫狼</strong><br />\n另外，前晚八時許，警方接獲四十二歲女事主報案，指她於本月九日傍晚，前往秀茂坪邨探訪南亞男友人時，在單位內遭對方胸襲非禮。事主聲稱與該名色狼僅認識三個月，事發前被對方巧言誘往上址侵犯。警方將案列為非禮處理，目前正追尋該名南亞漢下落，秀茂坪警區刑事調查隊接手追查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180323/00176_071.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180323%2F00176_071.html&d=9qwVmVD3aCsyYotQX9g%2BGzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=eed854b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180323/00176_071.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有南亞人埋身，非姦即盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b398a07021b2fced8ad1bf1237acd1cf887cfcfd","tid":603232,"uid":93839,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180323/photo/0323-00176-071b1.jpg?t=1521815516023\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180323%2Fphoto%2F0323-00176-071b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1521815516023&h=238ec293&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"530b0280fd2765cdfc55283fb3bc2464e1eae0c0","tid":603232,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"個別例子<br />\n我識有南亞人好好人有正職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05995003c46a816db2374cd72e892f45d96d3787","tid":603232,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"都係果句 南亞狗幾時比人滅種?"},{"pid":"00c6c5855b7bf3eaee31cd5f829bec7612a22a56","tid":603232,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef148179a16c2a4182957a88714f832f01f81825","tid":603232,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}